  <summary date="2015-02-02T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">VA Regional Office Accountability Act

Directs the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to include in a required annual report on Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) expenditures and activities a report on each VA regional office that failed to reach administrative goals concerning the timeliness and accuracy of veterans' claims adjudication.</summary>
